des:
Industrylift is empowering the Next Generation of working class.
We're building a purposeful network of entrepreneurs and workers of the steel industry, in order to investigate ways to lift up our industry.
We want to create a community of people motivated to work together, find, share and shape dreams, ideas and projects.
